data.description: This Completely Renovated 3 Bedroom, 3 Bath Rowhome by Building Character/MK Builders has a CHAP Tax Credit with around 5 Years Remaining. Enter this open concept home to the Bright Living Room featuring Crown molding, recessed lighting, ceiling fan and exposed brick and continue to the Dining Room and to the Gourmet Kitchen. Gleaming rich, dark Hardwood floors flow seamlessly through the Main and Upper levels. Entertaining is a delight in this Gourmet kitchen featuring sleek Stainless Steel Appliances including Gas Cooking, Granite Counters, white Shaker-style cabinets, Subway tile backsplash, Island with breakfast bar, Recessed lighting and door to the fully fenced courtyard patio with 6’ privacy fencing at the rear of the home. Make your way upstairs to find the Primary Bedroom Suite with Hardwood floors, ceiling fan, large wall closet and spacious Primary Bath with dual sink vanity and custom shower with subway tile surround. Also on this level is a Second Spacious Bedroom with Exposed Brick Accent Wall, Hall Full Bath with frameless glass shower door, waterfall shower head and tile flooring. Continue to delight your guests through the door to the Rooftop Deck with City and Water views. The Finished Lower Level features Bedroom 3 with carpeting, recessed lighting and a Full Bath with Tub/Shower combination and luxury vinyl plank flooring  This Gorgeous Renovated Home is located in the heart of Canton with plenty of Dining and Shopping, and a short walk to outdoor activities at Patterson Park and all of the activities on the water. This home offers the Best that City Living Has to Offer!
